      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WYONG KNOXVILLE (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (26.33) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Has ability and looks hard to stop. CHAIN DRIVE (8) turned in a fair run last time from the squeeze finishing fourth by 5 lengths (24.71). Key runner on best form. SNOW ROYALE (1) jumps from the inside draw. Last start finished 7th over 350m at Healesville beaten 5.5 lengths (20.07) behind Fred The Fox in a Grade 5 on June 5. Looks one of the chances. SHREK'S BROTHER (2) is right in the mix.",
